<!-- begin message 3 -->
<a name="3">
<table align="center" border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=2 width=100%>
  <tr>
	<td bgcolor="#707070" align="left">
		<font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica" color="#FFFFFF" size="1">
		<STRONG>CONTEST: Win a copy of the Ruins of Kunark expansion!</STRONG> []
		·· 04-12-2000 at 06:13 PM ·· ^<a href="#top">top</a></font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
	<td bgcolor="#202050">
	    <font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica" size="-2"><br>
		We are happy to announce we are giving away two copies of the Ruins of Kunark expansion!<p>To enter, submit either a Guide of some sort (class guide, trade guide, race guide, etc) or a fictional piece (story, lore piece, character bio, etc) between now and May 5 2000.  We'll judge them, and award a free copy of Ruins of Kunark to the best entry in each category (Guide or Fiction Piece).<p>There are no limits or minimums on length - all entries will be judged based on the quality of the entry itself.  Stories should, of course, be about characters, places, or events in the Everquest world.  If your story is from the point of view of a Good character, realize that it will be placed in the "Foe" section, as this is Neriak.COM, the home of the Teir'dal. :)<P> Winners will be announced on May 6, 2000.<p><STRONG>Email your submissions to <A HREF="mailto:keeper@neriak.com">keeper@neriak.com</A>.</STRONG><p><STRONG>NOTE:</STRONG> All entries that meet our requirements <EM>will</EM> be used on Neriak.COM regardless of whether or not they are the winning entry.  By entering the contest, you agree that your entry becomes property of Neriak.COM and will be used on the site.
		<p><font size="1">
		<STRONG>- <a href="mailto:keeper@neriak.com">The Keeper</a></STRONG></font></font></td>
  </tr>
